Your consent also allows us to transfer certain data to our partners for processing in third countries, especially in the USA (e.g., Google Analytics). For the USA, there is no adequacy decision of the EU Commission and despite extensive measures (see Cookie Policy), the high EU data protection level in the USA cannot be guaranteed. There are certain risks that transmitted data may not be deleted or further processed for any purpose, there may be disproportionate access to your data by US authorities and you may not be able to effectively enforce your rights in the US. However, you can access the "Cookie Settings" to make a specific choice. You can also revoke your consent at any time with effect for the future.
