http://optout.aboutads.info/?lang=EN&c=2#!%2F
You can also
download and install a browser add-on
if you wish to restrict the use of Google Analytics.
Changes and Contact
In order to comply with all legal requirements, this Cookie Policy is continuously adapted. You will always find the latest version on our website. We therefore recommend that you read this Cookie Policy each time you decide whether or not to accept Cookies from us. However, if required by applicable law, we will of course obtain your express consent to any material changes.
If you have any questions about the content of this Cookie Policy or the processing of your personal data, please contact our Data Protection Officer (via email to:
legal@blockpit.io
) or see our Privacy Policy. To ensure that personal data is only shared with the person concerned, we may require further identification data from you (e.g. passport, identity card, etc.).
